{"tid":1372042,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"(好撚嬲）下次合力拎警察對深藍活動發出反對通知書","createTime":"2019-07-27T10:57:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T12:09:25.000Z","uid":124100,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1b3eb6323184cf9defddc422c1c67b7c608fdab5","tid":1372042,"uid":124100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T10:57:51.000Z","msg":"曾正科又指截至今日警方已收到超過 1,700 名市民意見，反對警方發不反對通知書，另有 13 封元朗社區領袖的信件，對遊行安全表達關注。區議會曾對遊行表達憂慮，元朗校長會曾在電台表示擔憂，11 間大專校長亦呼籲學生不要參與。曾正科形容各界人士都強烈關注遊行安全問題，甚至是反對遊行 ...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/2328730767212530?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F2328730767212530%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=IcHW%2FfQ2zQNJFdNzTrXWKMeYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=aa41177b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/2328730767212530?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n有1700名市民反對，警察就發出反對通知書，咁到時有撐警或深藍活動，一人一封寫過去反對。<br />\n<br />\n好撚嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c11f2bbf246e3bed4a861ad51d870aa19667f431","tid":1372042,"uid":9328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T10:59:26.000Z","msg":"唔好天真，人地係黑社會有特權嫁"},{"pid":"9beb6ae76891c1911889c77c11b81914bb80cf4a","tid":1372042,"uid":232660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T12:09:25.000Z","msg":"不如扮支持警察搞個遊行好過 睇你點ban"}]}